snippet.title: A New Leaf: Memories - Kickstarter Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
A New Leaf : Memories is a 3D Farming Simulator. You wake up in a foreign island unable to recall anything. With only the basic tools for farming provided by the Town residents, regain your memories by completing quests and unfold your story.


A New Leaf: Memories on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ironheartstudios/a-new-leaf-memories



Source: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qjFSzGuuDOs


A New Leaf: Memories Website: https://www.anewleafgame.com
